    "created_at": "2012-09-25T19:34:42Z",
    "updated_at": "2012-09-25T19:34:42Z",
    "body": "`SingleThreaded` and `ManualThreads(1)` are identical. Calling `spawn_sched(ThreadPerCore)` will not cause the new tasks to go back to the default scheduler, it will create an entirely new scheduler for each call.\n",
